and so on.
<p>
<bf>TO TEST THE CHANGES</bf><p>
<tt>Do:</tt> access the ftp server using ftp client
<verb>
ftp www.you.com
</verb>
<p>
<tt>Should get:</tt>
ftp daemon should respond with prompt and version number!
